Super Snek

by: Alex Somich

This game was made for my level 2 project at The League of Amazing Programmers.
Click here to download and play!

1. Why I Made This Game

I decided to make this game because I like to play Snake, but my Snake game got messed up from the beginning of level 2. So I decided to remake the game of Snake and I added a Super Food, Evil food, and obstacles. Super Food makes you grow 1 and Evil Food makes you shrink 1. I decided to rename my game from the original boring Snake to Super Snek.

2. What I Learned

It really helps to have people test your game because otherwise you think your game is great, but it might not be as great to other people. Getting feedback from people how to make your game better really helps. It feels really good when you have someone come and try your game after you fix something and they say it's great!

3. Architecture of My Game

In my game I have many different classes that run my entire game. Each class has its own purpose. For example the Food class is in charge of all of the food and how they interact with the rest of my game. My obstacle class is in charge of where the obstacles are, the obstacles dimensions, and how they respond to being hit.

4. Technical Implementation

All of the objects in my game use collision boxes so when 2 collision boxes collide then you know 2 objects hit each other. I also have a constant timer always going so the game is always getting updated. I have 1 master class that all of the other smaller classes sent information to and then the master class runs everything.

5. Most Challenging Part

All of the objects in my game use collision boxes so when 2 collision boxes collide then you know 2 objects hit each other. I also have a constant timer always going so the game is always getting updated. I have 1 master class that all of the other smaller classes sent information to and then the master class runs everything.

6. Future Fixes and Updates

If I had a lot more time to work on my game I would make many levels that you move up when your get to a certain length. I would also make how the Snake moves a lot smoother and make the graphics more personalized.
